@startuml ReservationSequenceDiagram
title Create Appointment Reservation - Sequence Diagram (Simplified)

actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant ReservationService
participant SlotService
database Database

User -> Frontend : select slot + reserve
Frontend -> Backend : POST /reservations (slotId)

Backend -> ReservationService : createReservation(userId, slotId)

ReservationService -> SlotService : checkAvailability(slotId)
SlotService -> Database : get slot

Database --> SlotService : slot data
SlotService --> ReservationService : available

ReservationService -> Database : create reservation
ReservationService -> Database : update slot availability

Backend --> Frontend : success response
Frontend --> User : confirmation message

@enduml